that made me feel very seen.

00:04:22.200 --> 00:04:23.033
Thank you.
- [Tom] I got you, boo.

00:04:23.033 --> 00:04:24.510
- Asked for a favor?

00:04:24.510 --> 00:04:25.343
- Um.

00:04:27.540 --> 00:04:28.710
- He's lying, he's so needy.

00:04:28.710 --> 00:04:29.970
- Yeah.

00:04:29.970 --> 00:04:31.590
