to look after my dog.

00:04:31.590 --> 00:04:32.730
- That's a good one, though.
- Yeah.

00:04:32.730 --> 00:04:33.563
- The dog needs love.

00:04:33.563 --> 00:04:36.510
- Last time you emotionally
spiraled over a text?

00:04:36.510 --> 00:04:38.340
- Ooh, thankfully not in a while.

00:04:38.340 --> 00:04:39.240
Thank God for that.

00:04:39.240 --> 00:04:40.073
- [Tom] That's good.

00:04:40.073 --> 00:04:41.310
- I don't know, six months.

00:04:41.310 --> 00:04:43.260
Did something for the plot?

00:04:43.260 --> 00:04:44.251
- Did something just for the plot?

00:04:44.251 --> 00:04:45.084
- Just for the plot.

00:04:45.084 --> 00:04:46.642
Every time we go out to
dinner past a certain hour,

00:04:46.642 --> 00:04:47.804
it's, like we're doing it

00:04:47.804 --> 00:04:49.380
for the plot, you know?
- Yeah, yeah, yeah.

00:04:49.380 --> 00:04:51.690
Last time you screamed internally?

00:04:51.690 --> 00:04:53.250
