00:04:54.820 --> 00:04:55.927
[light music]
Round five, guess the look.

00:04:55.927 --> 00:04:57.180
- [Tom] Guess the look.

00:04:57.180 --> 00:04:58.162
- Oh, I didn't know

00:04:58.162 --> 00:04:59.820
