- This is fun.

00:04:59.820 --> 00:05:01.350
- You better lock in.

00:05:01.350 --> 00:05:02.183
- Where's this from?

00:05:02.183 --> 00:05:03.016
- I have to guess it.

00:05:03.016 --> 00:05:03.849
- Right, yeah.

00:05:03.849 --> 00:05:05.090
- Okay.
[Emily chuckling]

00:05:05.090 --> 00:05:07.920
- That is like, one of the
first proper red carpets I did,

00:05:07.920 --> 00:05:09.330
and it was the first ever premiere

00:05:09.330 --> 00:05:10.710
of season one of "Billy the Kid."

00:05:10.710 --> 00:05:12.720
- The answer is, ooh, "Billy the Kid."

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:13.788
He's such a baby.

00:05:13.788 --> 00:05:14.683
- [Tom] I'm a baby.

00:05:14.683 --> 00:05:15.640
- Look at your hair.

00:05:15.640 --> 00:05:16.950
- [Tom] A lot has happened since then.

00:05:16.950 --> 00:05:18.150
