00:05:30.550 --> 00:05:31.562
- [laughing] He's so scared.

00:05:31.562 --> 00:05:32.715
He's vibrating.

00:05:32.715 --> 00:05:34.680
- You make me so nervous.
- 'Cause the look is so good.

00:05:34.680 --> 00:05:35.513
- Yeah.

00:05:35.513 --> 00:05:36.346
- It was a really cool pantsuit,

00:05:36.346 --> 00:05:39.576
and they let me keep the glasses,
which was so nice of them.

00:05:39.576 --> 00:05:40.409
- [Tom] Nice, that's cool.

00:05:40.409 --> 00:05:41.280
- Yeah, this is gonna be much tougher.

00:05:41.280 --> 00:05:44.190
This is a slight pastels going on.

00:05:44.190 --> 00:05:46.830
- That's AMI, it's head to toe AMI,

00:05:46.830 --> 00:05:49.080
