jacket and a windbreaker,

00:06:43.350 --> 00:06:45.480
and I was fricking sweating.

00:06:45.480 --> 00:06:46.739
Anything for the fashion.

00:06:46.739 --> 00:06:47.633
- For the fashion.

00:06:48.510 --> 00:06:50.250
- This is a tricky one.

00:06:50.250 --> 00:06:51.390
Guess the look.

00:06:51.390 --> 00:06:54.330
- Oh, that's like a boob part.

00:06:54.330 --> 00:06:55.440
That's a boob cover. [laughing]

