London press for "My Lady Jane,"

00:06:59.490 --> 00:07:01.560
which was like my first
press look for that show.

00:07:01.560 --> 00:07:02.393
Am I right?
- I believe,

00:07:02.393 --> 00:07:03.510
I believe you are right.

00:07:03.510 --> 00:07:04.860
- That's pretty good.

00:07:04.860 --> 00:07:06.240
I mean, for it just being.

00:07:06.240 --> 00:07:07.380
- You look wonderful.

00:07:07.380 --> 00:07:08.550
- High-five.
